WEBVTT

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:10.000
From the creators of Tangled and Wreck-It Ralph,
Disney. A carrot-nosed, coal-eyed snowman shuffles
up to a purple flower peeping out of deep snow.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:19.000
Hello. He takes a deep sniff.
His nose lands on a frozen pond.
A reindeer looks up and pants like a dog.

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:28.000
Seeing the reindeer slip on the ice,
the snowman smiles and moves toward him,
though actually he's running on the spot.

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:36.000
The reindeer falls on his chin.
The snowman uses his arm as a crutch.
The reindeer paddles his front legs head over heels.

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:45.000
The snowman crawls along the ice.
The reindeer does the breaststroke.
The snowman rolls his body, but flips onto his back.

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:51.000
The reindeer's tongue sticks to the ice.
The snowman, his head, twig arm,
and reindeer lips tug at the carrot.

00:00:51.000 --> 00:01:00.000
The carrot flies off and lands in soft snow.
The reindeer goes after it with the snowman
and his body parts hanging on his tail.

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:08.000
The snowman puts himself back together again
and glumly contemplates his noseless state.

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:17.000
The reindeer jams the carrot back in place
and pants like a proud puppy.
The snowman pats him with a thin stick arm.

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:26.000
Then he goes to sneeze.
He grabs his nose with both hands.
His head shoots off.

00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:30.000
Frozen. Coming this winter in 3D.
